The article discusses the designation of emergency requirements for funding as outlined in the Continuing Appropriations Act, 2024 and Other Extensions Act. This designation is in accordance with section 114(c) of the Act and section 251(b)(2)(A) of the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985. The memorandum from the Director of the Office of Management and Budget provides further details on this action. The article is written by Joseph R. Biden Jr., the President of the United States, and was published on September 30, 2023.